data.description: Gorgeous, Move-In Ready Single Story Home with 3 Car Tandem Garage, a Sparkling Keith Zars Pool, 4 Bedrooms, 3 Full Baths, and an Office in Gated Trinity Oaks! From the Fresh Paint Throughout to the Just Installed Granite Counters in the Kitchen to the New Carpet in the Secondary Bedrooms to the Elegant Plantation Shutters to the Upgraded Stainless Steel Appliances, this Home is Truly Turnkey! You will love cooking and baking in your Expansive Kitchen Featuring 42" Cabinets, your Walk-In Pantry, that Opens to the Spacious Family Room complete with Fireplace, Beautiful Flooring Overlooking your Private Pool. Oversized Laundry Room boasts shelving and cabinets, HUGE Garage offers Utility Sink and Water Softener! Retreat to your Primary Suite Offering a Spa-Like Master Bath with Walk-In Shower and a HUGE Walk-In Closet with freshly installed warm floors. Relax in your peaceful backyard complete with a spacious flagstone patio, an inviting pool, mature trees, and a storage shed. Excellent Community Amenities including Pool, Park, Food Truck Thursdays, and Gated Access. Outstanding Comal ISD and Zoned to New Pieper High School! No City Taxes!
